issue.title: Error catching: tweet already favourited/identical tweet.
issue.body: Attempting api.create_favorite() on a tweet that's already been favorited will return a TweepError, and we should ignore that tweet (don't reply to it)

issue.title: ARDUINO: integrate arduino into our twitter account
issue.body:
(possibility 1) Create a secondary python script that checks our (@Iambellebot) twitter for updates and displays them on the screen + lights.

(possibility 2) Hook up to tweets.py and display on LCD + lights whenever a tweet is sent out.
